<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1530592-i-ve-just-re-read-the-wonderfully-written">I&#39;ve just re-read the wonderfully written &quot;City of Thieves&quot; by David Benioff, thinking that it was the one that described the members of the Leningrad Orchestra playing music when they were almost starving, and that they played Schostakovich. But it wasn&#39;t in that book. I also read &quot;Madonnas of Leningrad a few years ago, but before I re-read it, can tell me if the Orchestra thing is in it? What book is it in???</a>
